room_title: Escape room "The Cabin" by Escape Artist Texas in Houston
review: My son had his 11th birthday party at Escape Artist Texas in The Cabin. The owner made it easy to book the party. We had use of a room for cake and presents before the challenge. Antonio, the staff member who assited us, gave the kids just enough of a hint when they got stuck. We had so much fun! We’ll be sure to return. Our entire experience couldn’t have been better.

room_title: Escape room "The Cabin" by Escape Artist Texas in Houston
review: My husband and I did the cabin tonight and loved it! We have done quite a few rooms and this one was pretty cool and different! Can’t wait for their next new room!

room_title: Escape room "The Cabin" by Escape Artist Texas in Houston
review: We just finished our first one called “The Cabin”. We had a blast! The staff was nice and helpful. Room was really neat. Can’t wait to try again!
